{"tid":2238463,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★百佳現金券---NGO只接受原有會員申請，即使即時入會，亦不一定有現金劵","createTime":"2020-10-11T07:02:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-11T12:05:07.000Z","uid":19454,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f01f1185974b4d74a3f5b4c9ab022ffba53e5ba8","tid":2238463,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T07:02:59.000Z","msg":"過去一周曾致電與超市合作的27間社福機構查詢現金券派發實況，大部份機構表明已登記完畢，不少機構明言只接受有服務個案求助人或會員申請；部份機構<span class=\"xx-large\">只接受原有會員申請，其餘市民即使即時入會，亦不一定有現金劵</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n市民李先生表示，自己本身是社福機構會員，惟該機構不在百佳合作的名單之上，他曾經向部份相關機構查詢，有機構告知己暫停招收新會員，他認為做法不公平。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/5447291/org/c5d7b1dd0d0ae158913d4e8946312d3a.jpg/bGkCzIpUegJ1j__WZprolmxv3wnOy2VhCjj_HAo4_xw?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F5447291%2Forg%2Fc5d7b1dd0d0ae158913d4e8946312d3a.jpg%2FbGkCzIpUegJ1j__WZprolmxv3wnOy2VhCjj_HAo4_xw%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=20a1f153&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/534315/%E4%BF%9D%E5%B0%B1%E6%A5%AD%E4%BA%8C%E6%9C%9F-%E7%99%BE%E4%BD%B3%E7%8F%BE%E9%87%91%E5%88%B8%E9%99%90%E7%A4%BE%E7%A6%8F%E6%A9%9F%E6%A7%8B%E7%94%B3%E9%A0%98-%E6%B0%91%E5%BB%BA%E8%81%AF%E7%B1%B2%E6%94%BE%E5%AF%AC%E4%BB%A5%E6%8A%BD%E7%B1%A4%E7%99%BC%E6%94%BE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%2583%2585%2F534315%2F%25E4%25BF%259D%25E5%25B0%25B1%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E4%25BA%258C%25E6%259C%259F-%25E7%2599%25BE%25E4%25BD%25B3%25E7%258F%25BE%25E9%2587%2591%25E5%2588%25B8%25E9%2599%2590%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E7%25A6%258F%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%25A7%258B%25E7%2594%25B3%25E9%25A0%2598-%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%25B1%25B2%25E6%2594%25BE%25E5%25AF%25AC%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E6%258A%25BD%25E7%25B1%25A4%25E7%2599%25BC%25E6%2594%25BE&d=bDSN5K49m9pAVz54ArwUla9osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=2a3fc4b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ww